snippet.title: Gigawing 2 Full Game Play 1080P 60FPS Sega Dreamcast
snippet.description: Thanks to a VGA to HDMI upscaler and the XRGB Mini Framemeister I can finally capture the highest quality gameplay for the Sega Dreamcast and Gigawing 2 looks amazing!
